displayName: Pirate Ship of the Great Merchant Acreo

parameters:
Clea: The guild master is calling for you. Please give up
and come with me.

Great Merchant Acreo: Persistent little girls...! I'll use
these brats as hostages and negotiate with the guild!

Great Merchant Acreo: I am not just an ordinary merchant, I
am the great merchant Acreo-sama! I will show you something
that will leave you in awe!

Great Merchant Acreo: Ugh... Fine... Let me talk to
Agonia...
Clea: Understood, I will guide you.
